        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1945-02-12T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1945-02-12T00:00:00-05:00" n="62" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d62">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">868.00/2–1245: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Greece</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">MacVeagh</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Athens</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1945-02-12">February 12,
                            1945</date>.<lb/>[Received February 12—10:45 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>166. See my 150 of February 7.<note n="39" xml:id="d62fn39">Not printed.</note> A
                    Government communiqué published in this morning’s papers announces that after a
                    session which lasted all night agreement was reached between the Government and
                    EAM at 4:30 this morning. Messrs. Macmillan and Deeper were present. The members
                    of the respective deputations and the Secretary of the Conference signed a
                    protocol in which they “declare that they have reached complete agreement on all
                    the matters discussed during the Conference, and that a detailed text of the
                    agreement is to be signed today at 1400 hours”.<note n="40" xml:id="d62fn40">For
                        English translation, see <hi rend="italic">infra</hi>.</note>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">MacVeagh</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
